      /**

produce postestimation graphs

@author Markus Schaffner

*/

// to be run after paramML.do

cap log close
log using "log/figures_postestgraph.smcl", replace smcl


predict beta_predict, equation(beta4)
predict gamma_predict, equation(gamma4)
predict sigma_predict, equation(sigma)
predict eta_predict, equation(eta4)

bysort subjectid: egen beta_avg = mean( beta_predict )
bysort subjectid: egen gamma_avg = mean( gamma_predict )
bysort subjectid: egen sigma_avg = mean( sigma_predict )
bysort subjectid: egen eta_avg = mean( eta_predict )

// gen parameters


// max sigma

sum beta_avg, detail
local beta_a = r(mean)
local beta_max = r(max)
local beta_min = r(min)

sum gamma_avg, detail
local gamma_a = r(mean)
local gamma_max = r(max)
local gamma_min = r(min)

sum sigma_avg, detail
local sigma_a = r(mean)
local sigma_max = r(max)
local sigma_min = r(min)

sum eta_avg
local eta = r(mean)

sum beta_avg if sigma_avg >= (`sigma_max' * 0.99999)
local beta_sigma = r(mean)

sum gamma_avg if sigma_avg > (`sigma_max' * 0.99999)
local gamma_sigma = r(mean)


#delimit ;

tw ( function y=`gamma_a'*exp(-`beta_a'*(1-x^`eta')/`eta'),  )
   ( function y=`gamma_sigma'*exp(-`beta_sigma'*(1-x^`eta')/`eta'), )
  	,
	note("")
  	legend(label(1 "avg x's") label(2 "max {&sigma}") ) 
	aspect(1)
 	scheme(s2mono)
	ysize(1) xsize(1)
	
	name(functional, replace)
	xtitle("obj. prob.") 
        ytitle("subj. prob.")
  	xla(0(0.1)1, grid) yla(0(0.1)1, angle(horizontal) grid) plotregion(margin(none))
  	;
#delimit cr

graph export "figures/function_sigma.eps", replace
graph export "figures/function_sigma.png", replace






sum beta_avg, detail
local beta_a = r(mean)
local beta_max = r(p99)
local beta_min = r(p1)

sum gamma_avg, detail
local gamma_a = r(mean)
local gamma_max = r(p99)
local gamma_min = r(p1)

sum eta_avg
local eta = r(mean)

sum beta_avg if gamma_avg > `gamma_max'
local beta_maxgamma = r(mean)

sum gamma_avg if beta_avg > (`beta_max' * 0.99999)
local gamma_maxbeta = r(mean)

sum gamma_avg if beta_avg < (`beta_min' * 0.99999)
local gamma_minbeta = r(mean)

sum beta_avg if gamma_avg > (`gamma_min' * 1.00001)
local beta_mingamma = r(mean)


di "`gamma_a' `beta_a' `eta'"
di "`gamma_max' `beta_maxgamma' `eta'"
di "`gamma_maxbeta' `beta_max' `eta'"
di "`gamma_min' `beta_mingamma' `eta'"
di "`gamma_minbeta' `beta_min' `eta'"

#delimit ;

tw ( function y=`gamma_a'*exp(-`beta_a'*(1-x^`eta')/`eta'),  )
   ( function y=`gamma_max'*exp(-`beta_maxgamma'*(1-x^`eta')/`eta'),  range( 0.0 0.93 )   )
   ( function y=`gamma_min'*exp(-`beta_mingamma'*(1-x^`eta')/`eta'),  )
  	,
	note("")
  	legend(label(1 "avg {&gamma}") label(2 "p(99) {&gamma} & {&beta}") label( 3 "p(1) {&gamma}")) 
	aspect(1)
 	scheme(s2mono)
	ysize(1) xsize(1)
	name(functional99, replace)
	xtitle("obj. prob.") 
        ytitle("subj. prob.")
  	xla(0(0.1)1, grid) yla(0(0.1)1, angle(horizontal) grid) plotregion(margin(none))
  	;
#delimit cr

graph export "figures/function99.eps", replace
graph export "figures/function99.png", replace
